      "name": "Rally",
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "gm": "",
          "value": "<p>Your army's leaders attempt to bolster the soldiers' morale and fight back the effects of fear and panic. Attempt a Morale check against a target enemy army of your choice.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> If your army is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.kingmaker-features.Item.aZImSBBmTHff2POP]{Routed}, it loses the routed condition. Reduce your army's @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.kingmaker-features.Item.7LMDwpVijK7x5Jst]{Shaken} condition by 2.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> Reduce your army's shaken condition by 1.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> Your attempt to rally backfires—increase your army's shaken condition by 1.</p>"
        },
        "rules": [],
